with joy and verve and poetry.

01:04:14.059 --> 01:04:17.478
The two sides of my own brain
were all jumbled up and cross-wired.

01:04:17.562 --> 01:04:19.522
While one side was being neglected

01:04:19.606 --> 01:04:23.275
the other was in paradise watching
our Bulls play like big-leaguers.

01:04:23.944 --> 01:04:27.279
We swept a four-game series at Kinston,
two games at Winston-Salem

01:04:27.364 --> 01:04:30.616
and kicked the holy shit
